data.description: SeaCliff Estates is a tucked-away pocket community in the heart of Desirable Gig Harbor. The unique layout at this home is ideal for all kinds of living situations. It could be a perfect multi-generational property, maybe a duplex? On entry, you'll be greeted by a two story foyer with a den or sitting room at the front. You'll wander down the hallway on real hardwoods, passing 1 bedroom and office/den toward the first level living and kitchen areas. There's a utility room at the back of the home. As you get upstairs you'll find the primary at the back of the home with a deck capturing Sound Views! There's 2 more living areas,  dining area, and a larger kitchen. Don't skip the 980sf garage with side entry! Come tour this incredible property!
